PURPOSE
-------
Identify which xval_*.m functions in CanlabCore actually fit and
cross-validate a multivariate predictive model (so should be refactored
to return a @predictive_model object), vs. which are CV utilities
(holdout selection, feature selection helpers, plotting) that should be
left alone for this phase.

CATEGORIES
----------
  A. PREDICTIVE-MODEL FITTER  -> refactor to return predictive_model
                                 (variable name: pmodel_obj)
  B. CV UTILITY               -> leave alone
  C. LEGACY / BACKUP          -> leave alone


